 53→/**
 54→ * Staggered initialization to prevent "thundering herd" problem when multiple tabs
 55→ * are restored simultaneously (e.g., after browser restart).
 56→ *
 57→ * Background tabs get a random delay (3-8s) to distribute initialization load.
 58→ * Foreground tabs initialize immediately for good UX.
 59→ *
 60→ * This prevents triggering Google's rate limiting when restoring sessions with
 61→ * many Gemini tabs containing long conversations.
 62→ */
