### 12. **Handling Different Menu Structures**

The code handles three distinct menu layouts:

| Layout | Selector | Structure | Notes |
|--------|----------|-----------|-------|
| **Desktop Standard** | `.mat-mdc-menu-panel.gds-mode-switch-menu[role="menu"]` | Material menu panel + menu items | Has `data-mode-id` attribute |
| **Mobile Compact** | `mat-action-list.gds-mode-switch-menu-list` | Bottom-sheet action list | Uses `jslog` metadata for ID fallback |
| **Generic Fallback** | `.mat-mdc-menu-panel[role="menu"]` | Material menu panel | Last resort, less reliable |

**Adaptive title selectors**:
- `.mode-title` (desktop)
- `.gds-title-m` (mobile)
